{"tid":336841,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"換新CPU開唔到機，求救！","createTime":"2017-07-26T18:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T06:05:13.000Z","uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aaea2f6c69c776987a6cfd974693d14c8bb0e091","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:12:59.000Z","msg":"原本配置如下：<br />\n底板：H61M-DS2 rev.2.2<br />\nCPU：Intel  i5-2320<br />\nHDD：日立500GB 7200轉(開機會有咔嚓幾聲，估計就快收皮)<br />\n顯示卡：Zontac GTX 1050Ti OC(早前連登巴打介紹換的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nRam：8GB x2(底板其中一個插槽比我插壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返8GB)<br />\n電源：iPower 85H  450w<br />\n<br />\n咁我今日收左隻二手i7-2600同買左隻雜牌CPU風扇，裝完之後開機冇畫面，mon顯示無訊號，風扇有轉，底板冇響任何Be聲，紅燈暗暗地長著(係咪叫處理燈)。試過蚊走顯示卡，插底板VGA都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外已經升左最新Bios。插返隻i5-2320又一切正常。<br />\n<br />\n安慰下自己如果假設隻i7冇壞，仲有咩可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cd6112e126682226ed5e228467d74acc32cba3","tid":336841,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"淘寶二手壞件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2c0431184346ee21ba7a5c2fb1e9ee28e1d4a5","tid":336841,"uid":56328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"散熱膏太多/散熱器裝得唔好"},{"pid":"4d9f06ec6632e76122a1c752d45dd2b13b9bd02e","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘寶二手壞件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67349e438a51d1c7cfc5b0a2a445c6c484ec217","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>散熱膏太多/散熱器裝得唔好</blockquote><br />\n散熱膏我好似真係整多左少少，但係會至於咁嚴重？完全開唔到機？我用粒i5-2320都正常開機啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2e5bddbb18ac96f30ede54229c881b3e286175","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/023415_96a31b3ff83c47eb53cd6e843d64fc39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F023415_96a31b3ff83c47eb53cd6e843d64fc39.jpg&h=3416a1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/023417_c4dbefa1ac269f714b610f909ba7e0e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F023417_c4dbefa1ac269f714b610f909ba7e0e3.jpg&h=f3394117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齋睇表面係咪唔會睇得出有咩異樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea24ad0f76c2d1455b31eda7de91a870841a53c3","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘寶二手壞件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想換部新，只想升級下，啱用嘅CPU好似得二手可以揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07b7daead155aae1a03071de00f04bdd22c04e7","tid":336841,"uid":59734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:42:56.000Z","msg":"問人借隻牛試試佢"},{"pid":"2e43b198a99da99452b7c84b4b171698f8a4f40b","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問人借隻牛試試佢</blockquote><br />\n但係我用i5-2320可以正常開機，真係關隻牛事？<br />\n比我插壞左一條Ram槽，打算聽日去買過塊板順便試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506ead780d6e725f13b1be73a8a30269198ae62f","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:45:25.000Z","msg":"聽人講CPU好難壞，咁都比我收到隻壞的話，係咪應該去買六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7882dd4184f9c2947fc5f358fe4ecf922d3ac7","tid":336841,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽人講CPU好難壞，咁都比我收到隻壞的話，係咪應該去買六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能佢特登賣隻壞左嘅CPU比你哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aef74b6ebceb75d6facb97d80874f4151186ec3","tid":336841,"uid":130706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T22:29:51.000Z","msg":"係咪裝得唔好呀 影塊底板黎睇下"},{"pid":"48338bfb3f01ce0c3a7bbd6e1156e1e181a94e3d","tid":336841,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T23:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽人講CPU好難壞，咁都比我收到隻壞的話，係咪應該去買六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔比係人地超到燒左先放出黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw,有冇上網check過老母板用唔用到依粒U?"},{"pid":"338f4eacbcad29e243e688e4c74d93046d7feb80","tid":336841,"uid":92702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽人講CPU好難壞，咁都比我收到隻壞的話，係咪應該去買六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔比係人地超到燒左先放出黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw,有冇上網check過老母板用唔用到依粒U?</blockquote><br />\n都冇k⋯⋯⋯上網check話ok啊，同樣係LGA1155插口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"